&lt;p>Sanatan Dharma Values and beliefs are &lt;br>
Every human takes birth because in their previous Life, &lt;br>
that soul was human but couldn&amp;rsquo;t get Moksha &lt;br>
Or from previous millions of life evolution you became human first time. &lt;br>
Whatever you do, whatever you celebrate or enjoy, &lt;br>
and whatever you achieve while you are living &lt;br>
the ultimate goal of life is Moksha or Nirvana, or Kaivalya.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>